sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Website as AI-Solutions Website
    participant API as Backend API
    participant DB as MongoDB Database
    participant ImageStore as Image Assets
    actor Admin

    User->>Website: Open public website
    Website->>API: Request published content
    API->>DB: Fetch services, projects, articles, events, gallery and reviews
    DB-->>API: Return content
    API-->>Website: Send public content
    Website-->>User: Display website pages

    User->>Website: Open event detail page
    Website->>API: Request selected event
    API->>DB: Fetch event details and cover image URL
    API-->>Website: Send event details
    Website->>ImageStore: Load uploaded event image
    ImageStore-->>Website: Return image file
    Website-->>User: Show full event details

    User->>Website: Submit inquiry form
    Website->>API: Send inquiry details
    API->>API: Validate form data
    API->>DB: Save inquiry
    DB-->>API: Inquiry saved
    API-->>Website: Show success response

    Admin->>Website: Login to admin panel
    Website->>API: Send credentials
    API->>DB: Verify admin account
    DB-->>API: Return admin data
    API->>API: Compare hashed password and create token
    API-->>Website: Send JWT token
    Website-->>Admin: Open admin dashboard

    Admin->>Website: Open inquiry handling page
    Website->>API: Request inquiries
    API->>DB: Fetch inquiry records
    DB-->>API: Return inquiry records
    API-->>Website: Send inquiry list
    Website-->>Admin: Display inquiries

    Admin->>Website: Update inquiry status or delete inquiry
    Website->>API: Send update request
    API->>DB: Update database record
    DB-->>API: Update completed
    API-->>Website: Return updated data
    Website-->>Admin: Display updated result

    Admin->>Website: Export inquiry CSV
    Website->>API: Request CSV export
    API->>DB: Fetch inquiry export data
    DB-->>API: Return inquiry data
    API-->>Website: Download CSV file
    Website-->>Admin: Save CSV file

    Note over Admin,Website: If admin is inactive for more than 2 minutes
    Website-->>Admin: Logout and redirect to login page
